title: Watch: SF9 Shares Dance Practice Video For "Roar" | Soompi
text:
Display.Sharethrough.Soompi.1x1 
SF9 has given fans a full look at the choreography for their latest track “Roar”! 
On February 22, the nine-member group from FNC Entertainment proved once again why they’re known for their dancing talents by releasing a practice video for their powerful song “Roar.” 
The track is off their first ever mini album, entitled “Burning Sensation,” which was released on February 6 along with the stunning music video for “Roar.” 
Watch the guys practice “Roar” below!
